spanGrp.span: nam longbini nap pune punen soo
I want to tell a story
punen kiye mu usilii vaven soo són san yaapuo
this story is about a woman and her husband
stori ya abaot wan woman wetem man blong hem
kolom du van, san vanmoro mo sógó saloo waawaa soo
the two lived on, his woman was pregnant with a child
tufala i stap gogo, woman blong hem i gat bel blong wan pikinini blong tufala
mwe van, mwi lingi san waawaa
so, she gave birth to her baby
i go, i putum bebe blong hem
pán em ne meseen, san waawaa me e timaleh man
in the hospital, the baby was a boy
long hospital, bebe blong hem emi wan boe
bili ke mu kuoli, me mee, kolom du
when she came back, the two lived on
taem we i kambak, i kam, tufula i stap
van, timaleh me mee mo bo, san naana me met
so, the child grew, his mother died
i go, pikinini i kam bigwan, mama blong hem i ded
san naana me met, timaleh man són san taati gon kolom du
his mother died, the small boy with his father only stayed
mama blong hem i ded, smol boe wetem papa blong hem tufala i stap
with his father, the two stayed
wetem blong hem tufala i stap
teman mo longbini ka be van bi mini liibweyee
his father wanted to go drink kava
papa blong hem i wantem go drink kava
bili ke me van, mwe vehe san timaleh, kolom du
when he went, he carried his chiild, the two stayed
taem we i go, i karem pikinini blong hem, tufala i stap
bili ke mi mini liibweyee, mwi lingi naren mwe pwet pán yee soo
when he drank kava, he put his child under a tree
taem i dring kava, i putum pikinini blong hem i stap andanit wan tri
san teman mi mini liibweyee, van, mo lotmiyene timaleh mwe pwet
the father drank kava, and so he forgot about the child
papa blong hem i dring kava gogo, i fogetem pikinini i stap
bili ke timaleh mwe pwetmalek, temát soo me mee mwi idi
when the child was asleep, a demon came and took it
taem pikinini i silip, wan devel i kam tekem hem
he carried the child, the two went away
i karem pikinini, tufala i go
kolom van, mwe vehe mwe pwet lan bot velan lamwiye
the two went, he carried him, he stayed on top of his shoulder
tufala i go, i karem i stap long solda blong hem antap
mu du mu du kolom duusili silii kolom van, timaleh mwe téé mwe lehe yee soo mwe pwetkoró ot
the two followed the road, the child saw a branch across the road
tufala i folem rod tufala i go, pikinini i luk wan wud i krosem ples
timaleh me mela, mu gumgare yee mwe pólo van, mwe pwet lamwiye
the child jumped, grasping the branch, and went up and stayed on top
pikinini i jam, i holem taet wud, i klaem i go i stap antap
mwe deme ka timaleh kiye te pwet lan bot velan gon
he thought that the child was sitting on his shoulder
hem i ting se pikinini ya i stap long solda blong hem nomo
timaleh kiye, teman, bili ke mi mini liibweyee van monok, mwe deme san timaleh
the child, his father, when he finished drinking kava, he thought about his child
pikinini ya, papa blong hem, taem we i dring kava finis, i dingbaot pikinini blong hem
me van mwe tééne san timaleh, san timaleh mwe pwet toót
he went and looked for his child, but his child was lost
i go i luk pikinini blong hem, be pikinini blong hem i lus
he kept looking out for him
he followed the road, he went on
mwe lehe ke naren man mo pólopwet lan yee
he saw that his boy stayed on the branch
i luk pikinini blong hem i klaem i stap long wud
he took his boy from the tree
i karem aot pikinini blong hem
mwe vehe me mee, kolom van tyenem
he carried him and came, the two went home
i karem i kam, tufala i go long haos
temát me mee, mwe tééne timaleh, tere lese
the demon came and looked for the child, he did not see him
devel i kam, i lukaotem pikinini, i no luk
timaleh teman mwe vehe, kolom van monok
the child, his father carried him, the two went, finish
pikini papa blong hem i karem, tufala i go finis
kiye gon me e sok punen me metmet, nam longbini nap pune
this is the my short story that I want to tell
emya nomo i sot stori blong mi, mi wantem talem
